\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15138,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/19\/vanity-garments\/","url_meta":{"origin":43164,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Vanity: Humiliation for clothing in ostentation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 19, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever wears a garment in vanity, Allah will make him wear a garment of humiliation on the Day of Resurrection, then He will set it ablaze with fire.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Majah 3607 Grade: Hasan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32376,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/19\/earth-swallows-man-pride\/","url_meta":{"origin":43164,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Vanity: Earth swallows man dragging his garment","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhile a man was trailing his robe out of vanity, he was suddenly swallowed up, and he will be buried in the earth until the Day of Resurrection.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5790 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonli